{"title": "Mare au diable", "description": "Sur l'avis de son beau-p\u00e8re, malgr\u00e9 sa r\u00e9ticence, le laboureur Germain, veuf de vingt-huit ans, va se rendre \u00e0 Fourche pour rencontrer celle qui deviendra peut-\u00eatre la nouvelle m\u00e8re de ces trois petits enfants, la fille du p\u00e8re L\u00e9onard, jeune veuve elle aussi. <br/>Apprenant ce d\u00e9placement, la m\u00e8re Guillette demande qu'il emm\u00e8ne avec lui sa fille, Marie, qui s'en va travailler comme berg\u00e8re dans la r\u00e9gion. <br/>En cours de route, la nuit tombe. Le brouillard se l\u00e8ve et les voil\u00e0 perdus, dans les bois, au bord d'une mare... <br /><br />His father-in-law insisting upon it, Germain goes to Fourche to meet a young widow who might become the new mother of his three children. <br/>Doing so, he accompanies Marie, a young girl from his village, who is going to work on a farm in that area. <br/>As the night comes, they get lost in a wood, next to a pool...<br />(Summary by Ezwa)", "duration": 12603, "language": "French", "authors": [{"id": "1055", "name": "George Sand"}], "coverArt": "https://www.archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCovers3/mareaudiable_1008.jpg", "copyright_year": "1846", "genres": ["Romance"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Ezwa"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Ezwa"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Ezwa"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Bernard"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Notice", "readers": [123], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/la_mare_au_diable_ezwa_librivox/mareaudiable_00_sand_64kb.mp3", "duration": 137}, {"section": 1, "title": "1 - L'auteur au lecteur", "readers": [123], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/la_mare_au_diable_ezwa_librivox/mareaudiable_01_sand_64kb.mp3", "duration": 437}, {"section": 2, "title": "2 - Le labour", "readers": [123], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/la_mare_au_diable_ezwa_librivox/mareaudiable_02_sand_64kb.mp3", "duration": 930}, {"section